<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head profile="http://gmpg.org/xfn/11"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /><title> 10 Reasons You Should Never Get a Job</title><meta name="generator" content="WordPress" /><link rel="stylesheet" href="http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/wp-content/themes/pavlina/style.css" type="text/css" media="screen" /><link rel="stylesheet" href="http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/wp-content/themes/pavlina/print.css" type="text/css" media="print" /><link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="RSS 2.0" href="http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/feed/" /><link rel="alternate" type="text/xml" title="RSS .92" href="http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/feed/rss/" /><link rel="alternate" type="application/atom+xml" title="Atom 0.3" href="http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/feed/atom/" /><link rel="pingback" href="http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/xmlrpc.php" /><link rel='archives' title='December 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/12/' /><link rel='archives' title='November 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/11/' /><link rel='archives' title='October 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/10/' /><link rel='archives' title='September 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/09/' /><link rel='archives' title='August 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/08/' /><link rel='archives' title='July 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/07/' /><link rel='archives' title='June 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/06/' /><link rel='archives' title='May 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/05/' /><link rel='archives' title='April 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/04/' /><link rel='archives' title='March 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/03/' /><link rel='archives' title='February 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/02/' /><link rel='archives' title='January 2010' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2010/01/' /><link rel='archives' title='December 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/12/' /><link rel='archives' title='November 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/11/' /><link rel='archives' title='October 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/10/' /><link rel='archives' title='September 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/09/' /><link rel='archives' title='August 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/08/' /><link rel='archives' title='July 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/07/' /><link rel='archives' title='June 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/06/' /><link rel='archives' title='May 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/05/' /><link rel='archives' title='April 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/04/' /><link rel='archives' title='March 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/03/' /><link rel='archives' title='February 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/02/' /><link rel='archives' title='January 2009' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2009/01/' /><link rel='archives' title='December 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/12/' /><link rel='archives' title='November 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/11/' /><link rel='archives' title='October 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/10/' /><link rel='archives' title='September 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/09/' /><link rel='archives' title='August 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/08/' /><link rel='archives' title='July 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/07/' /><link rel='archives' title='June 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/06/' /><link rel='archives' title='May 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/05/' /><link rel='archives' title='April 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/04/' /><link rel='archives' title='March 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/03/' /><link rel='archives' title='February 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/02/' /><link rel='archives' title='January 2008' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2008/01/' /><link rel='archives' title='December 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/12/' /><link rel='archives' title='November 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/11/' /><link rel='archives' title='October 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/10/' /><link rel='archives' title='September 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/09/' /><link rel='archives' title='August 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/08/' /><link rel='archives' title='July 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/07/' /><link rel='archives' title='June 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/06/' /><link rel='archives' title='May 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/05/' /><link rel='archives' title='April 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/04/' /><link rel='archives' title='March 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/03/' /><link rel='archives' title='February 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/02/' /><link rel='archives' title='January 2007' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2007/01/' /><link rel='archives' title='December 2006' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2006/12/' /><link rel='archives' title='November 2006' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2006/11/' /><link rel='archives' title='October 2006' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2006/10/' /><link rel='archives' title='September 2006' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2006/09/' /><link rel='archives' title='August 2006' href='http://www.stevepavlina.com/blog/2006/08/' /><link rel='archives' title='July 2006' href='http://www.stevep